title: 11/29: Start or Sit (AFC Home Games) (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Let's get into some rankings debates (1:30) with Philip Rivers, Dion Lewis, LeSean McCoy and more ... News and notes (15:15) plus the Startometer (23:48) for Derrick Henry, Kenyan Drake, Mike Williams and a few others ... MIN-NE (24:45), CLE-HOU (30:10), IND-JAC (33:42), DEN-CIN (37:50), LAC-PIT (43:30), NYJ-TEN (47:35), BUF-MIA (50:00), KC-OAK (52:00) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
